{
  "stem": "6719.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the man in charge down there-- all-- not only there, but in charge of all five crematoriums were Hauptscharfuhrer Otto Moll, M-O-L-L, the cyclops.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He had one eye, one glass eye.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And behind his [? bag, ?] he was it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I mean, this is mister-- if you talk about Auschwitz, you talk about Otto Moll.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was the guy that, uh-- [SIGHS] there, I saw some Sonderkommando, never at work but I saw-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] apparently what happened was that, uh, the capacity for, uh, gas people was enough.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But the cremation facilities weren't large enough, and they worked day and night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the reason that we went down there, uh, were to fix the roof because the shingles took off around the-- the chimney.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we walked in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Otto Moll gave us a reception and told us in no uncertain terms, first of all everybody's a swine.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That's the address that we received, [? wir ?] schweine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Anybody's looking around himself, I'm a good shot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then he just pointed his pistol and shot a guy down there-- from the sonderkommando-- right in his leg, or in his hip, or something, just to show us what kind of a hero he was with-- with how-- how well he can handle a gun.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we are put on the roof.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Uh, curiosity kills the cat, and as a human being, every human, you're curious, no matter how dangerous it may be, or how rough the surroundings, or how somebody threatens you.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It's like somebody say close your eyes, and you just go like through and he think your eyes are closed, but then you see something.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
